  "description": "<h3>Back of Case - Nintendo DS (UK) (from <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/beat-the-intro/adblurbs\">Ad Blurbs</a>)</h3><h3>Challenge yourself and your friends with &quot;BEAT THE INTRO&quot; the 1st Music Quiz Game on Nintendo DS!</h3>\nPlay this fast paced music quiz with a full range of music based games for everyone! Can you identify some of the best selling music tracks from the past six decades? Can you complete famous song lyrics or reveal major artists by re-arranging their photos?<br><br>Songs from the 1960's-2000's<br><br>(screenshot captions)\n<ul>\n<li>Test your musical knowledge on more than 1,900 tracks and questions!</li>\n<li>Spin records like a DJ using the Nintendo DS stylus to recognize a song.</li>\n<li>With &quot;Head to Head&quot; mode  you can play against a friend with just a Nintendo DS single-card!</li>\n</ul>",
